{"tid":2372050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港100單: 花市照開。台灣4單: 燈會停開","createTime":"2021-01-19T10:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T06:56:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"54e9821be770365ff359e65b6605427769bcf678","tid":2372050,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571216-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571216-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=7abfdbaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571216-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e472c3a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571216-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣桃園醫院疫情擴大，新增4人確診，包括2宗是早前確診醫生同住的家人，1人為工作的密切接觸者，另外1宗為住院病人的外籍看護。<br />\n<br />\n台灣累計有868宗確診。<br />\n<br />\n因應本土疫情升溫，行政院宣布，停辦下月的燈會，這是燈會1990年創辦以來，首次停辦。今年燈會原定下月26日至3月7日在新竹舉行。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳時中完全技術擊倒"},{"pid":"40d333b1466180c1ff068504ecb8cc00b3953718","tid":2372050,"uid":238415,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"台灣真係抗疫<br />\n香港係政治任務黎<br />\n咁樣黎比較其實真係無咩意思"},{"pid":"a74f38812fe0cc39a95cd4ae5657a3f5858fdcbd","tid":2372050,"uid":74163,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂 廢病一個<br />\n起馬多返樣娛樂先<br />\n不過其實要開返曬堂食先合理"},{"pid":"0b31a8556bf401d129378153d4832620794abe31","tid":2372050,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"40d333b1466180c1ff068504ecb8cc00b3953718","tid":2372050,"uid":238415,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"台灣真係抗疫<br />\n香港係政治任務黎<br />\n咁樣黎比較其實真係無咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"香港係打壓"},{"p